==Russian==

===Indefinite pronoun===
'''что-то''' (štó-to)
:'''N.B.''' &mdash; the particle [[-то]] imparts a sense of indefiniteness similar to English [[some]]. The forms of '''что-то''' are usually associated with affirmatives (like [[something]]), while [[что-нибудь]] is associated with questions and negatives (like [[anything]]).

# [[something]]
#:*{{RUchar|Я [[видеть|ви́жу]] что́-то!}} — ''I see something!''
#:*{{RUchar|[[видеть|Ви́дите]] [[ли]] [[вы]] [[что-нибудь|что́-нибудь]]?}} — ''Do you see anything?''

